---
import designedBuildingsImg from '../../../assets/Images/SolutionImg/Designes/DesignedBuildings.png';
import designedBuildingsTwoImg from '../../../assets/Images/SolutionImg/Designes/DesignedBuildingsTwo.png';
import pegienImg from '../../../assets/Images/SolutionImg/Designes/Pegien.png';
import affordableImg from '../../../assets/Images/SolutionImg/Designes/OurProfessionalism/Affordable.png';
import clothHangerImg from '../../../assets/Images/SolutionImg/Designes/OurProfessionalism/ClothHangerDesigns.png';
import commitmentImg from '../../../assets/Images/SolutionImg/Designes/OurProfessionalism/CommitmentToFamily.png';
import customSolutionsImg from '../../../assets/Images/SolutionImg/Designes/OurProfessionalism/CoustomSolutions.png';
import expertInstallationImg from '../../../assets/Images/SolutionImg/Designes/OurProfessionalism/ExpectInstallation.png';
import extensiveExperienceImg from '../../../assets/Images/SolutionImg/Designes/OurProfessionalism/ExtensiveExperience.png';
import fastProfessionalImg from '../../../assets/Images/SolutionImg/Designes/OurProfessionalism/FastAndProfessional.png';
import ProfessionalCall from '../../../assets/Icons/SolutionIcons/ProfessionalsIcons/professionalCall.png';
---

<section class="professionals-section">
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Invisible Grill for Balconies Section -->
        <div class="balcony-section">
            <h2>Invisible Grill for Balconies</h2>
            
            <div class="content-grid">
                <div class="image-section">
                    <div class="main-image">
                        <img src={designedBuildingsImg.src} alt="Designed For High-Rise Living" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="side-images">
                        <img src={designedBuildingsTwoImg.src} alt="Building design" />
                        <img src={pegienImg.src} alt="Pigeon protection" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="text-content">
                    <div class="paragraphs-wrapper">
                        <p>Invisible Grills for balconies provide a perfect blend of safety, security, and <br> aesthetic appeal, making them an ideal choice for modern homes and <br> commercial spaces. These grills are designed to offer protection without <br>compromising the view, creating an unobstructed and seamless appearance.<br> Made with high-tensile strength stainless steel wires, invisible grills are highly <br> durable and resistant to corrosion, ensuring long-lasting performance.</p>
                        
                        <p>The minimalistic design of invisible grills complements various architectural<br> styles, whether it's a contemporary or traditional setting. With custom-sized<br> installations, these grills can be fitted to any balcony or window, providing a<br> secure barrier that prevents accidental falls, especially for children and pets.</p>
                        
                        <p>Invisible grills are highly space-efficient and do not clutter or obstruct the<br> open feeling of your balcony. Their wire spacing is designed to be discreet yet<br> secure, offering a high level of protection while maintaining the visual appeal<br> of the surrounding area. Additionally, their UV-resistant coating ensures that<br> they remain attractive and functional, even in harsh weather conditions.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <button class="enquiry-btn">Enquiry Now <img src={ProfessionalCall.src} alt="Call Icon" class="btn-icon" /></button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Our Professionalism Section -->
        <div class="professionalism-section">
            <h2>Our Professionalism</h2>
            
            <div class="cards-scroll">
                <div class="cards-track">
                    <img src={expertInstallationImg.src} alt="Expert installation" />
                    <img src={customSolutionsImg.src} alt="Custom solutions" />
                    <img src={fastProfessionalImg.src} alt="Fast and professional" />
                    <img src={affordableImg.src} alt="Affordable" />
                    <img src={clothHangerImg.src} alt="Cloth Hanger Designs" />
                    <img src={commitmentImg.src} alt="Commitment To Family" />
                    <img src={extensiveExperienceImg.src} alt="Extensive Experience" />
                    <img src={expertInstallationImg.src} alt="Expert installation" />
                    <img src={customSolutionsImg.src} alt="Custom solutions" />
                    <img src={fastProfessionalImg.src} alt="Fast and professional" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .professionals-section {
        padding: 80px 0;
        background: #f8f8f8;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 1400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 40px;
    }

    .balcony-section {
        margin-bottom: 80px;
    }

    .balcony-section h2 {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        font-size: 36px;
        font-weight: 400;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .content-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 0.4fr;
        gap: 40px;
        align-items: start;
    }

    .image-section {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0;
    }

    .main-image {
        position: relative;
        border-radius: 16px;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .main-image img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 550px;
        object-fit: contain;
    }


    .side-images {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 15px;
    }

    .side-images img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 300px;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 16px;
    }

    .text-content {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        padding-top: 120px;
    }

    .paragraphs-wrapper {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 24px;
    }

    .text-content p {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #666;
        margin: 0;
        white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .enquiry-btn {
        background: transparent;
        border: 2px solid #D4A574;
        color: #D4A574;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border-radius: 25px;
        font-size: 16px;
        cursor: pointer;
        margin-top: 24px;
        align-self: flex-start;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
    }

    .btn-icon {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        object-fit: contain;
    }

    .enquiry-btn:hover {
        background: #D4A574;
        color: white;
    }

    .professionalism-section h2 {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        font-size: 36px;
        font-weight: 400;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .cards-scroll {
        overflow: hidden;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .cards-track {
        display: flex;
        gap: 30px;
        animation: scrollLeft 25s linear infinite;
        width: max-content;
    }

    @keyframes scrollLeft {
        0% { transform: translateX(0); }
        100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }
    }

    .cards-track:hover {
        animation-play-state: paused;
    }

    .cards-track img {
        width: auto;
        height: 280px;
        object-fit: contain;
        border-radius: 16px;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }
</style>